				"synopsis": {
					"type": 23,
					"value": "Jaheira's middle daughter that is inside - she's earnest and friendly.\r\n\r\nShe's discovered Jaheira's links to nobility in Tethyr and is playing up the idea she might be born of a royal line -- playing princess. The player can play along or puncture the whole thing."
